name: Warung Babi Guling Bu Ari
address: Jl. Raya Payangan No.26, Puhu, Kec. Payangan, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80572, Indonesia
review 1:
if you go to Batur via Payangan roads, this place is a must to visit to fill your hunger, i buy the 20.000idr portion and its worth.

the place is clean, the taste is rich, so delicious
review 2: Randomly stopped because we were hungry on our way to Kintamani. Surprisingly tasty food. Looks like it's popular amongst the locals because the place got crowded while we were eating.
review 3: Food was average, too spicy for me and I could not taste anything as too spicy...for you if you like spicy Babi guling this place might be your choice, but if you don't like spicy food, I do not recommend this place
review 4: I have taste this babi guling twice and it have a nice taste with affordable price. It located near Padma resort so its a very convinience for guest of this hotel to buy dinner since not much restaurant open in that area.
review 5:
Sangat enak disini.

If you like to try real Balinese food, this Warung can be recommended.
